v 3
d un_pop - UN WPP2024 population estimates and projections for one or more countries
d
d un_pop loads one row per country x year x 5-year age group x sex,
d stacking historical estimates with the chosen UN projection variant and
d merging in country identifiers, straight from GitHub or a local mirror.
d
d Distribution-Date: 02Jul2026
d Author: Eduard Bukin, ebukin@worldbank.org
d Support: email ebukin@worldbank.org

